message: Hey Bob, did you reach out to ABC Consulting?
Not yet, I'll do that right away.
Bob, can you also send the proposal to XYZ Corp?
Sure thing, I'll have it ready by EOD.
I’m still waiting on their feedback. I’ll follow up with them today.
ok, lets create some marketing collateral and start reach outs @Charlie

a deck and some social media posts to start with
Great! I can draft the deck. How many slides are you thinking?
How about a 10-slide deck? That should cover the key points without overwhelming them.
Once the deck is ready, I can help with the social media posts. Do you have any specific platforms in mind?
